- Use CDK-Nag to enforce security best practices in your CDK constructs
- Implement custom rules to address project-specific security requirements
- Regularly update CDK-Nag to benefit from the latest security checks
- Use suppression judiciously and document the reasons for suppressing warnings
- Integrate CDK-Nag into your CI/CD pipeline for automated security checks
- Only validate against NIST 800-53 rev 5 ruleset
